OL,3,CWaspi campaigners call for a vote in
OL,4,CParliament on compensation
OL,6,FWaspi women have campaigned for
OL,7,Fsupport for those born in the 1950s,
OL,8,Fsaying they did not receive sufficient
OL,9,Fwarning of the state pension age for
OL,10,Fwomen being raised from 60 to 65, in
OL,11,Fline with men.
OL,13,FThose affected were initially told
OL,14,Fthey would not receive state pension
OL,15,Fcompensation in December 2024.
