OL,3,CWaspi campaigners call for a vote in
OL,4,CParliament on compensation
OL,6,FIn November last year, Work and
OL,7,FPensions Secretary Pat McFadden said
OL,8,Fthe government would reconsider this
OL,9,Fdecision after the emergence of new
OL,10,F"evidence" which his predecessor, Liz
OL,11,FKendall, was not shown.
OL,13,FBut last week, McFadden said: "The
OL,14,Fevidence shows that the vast majority
OL,15,Fof 1950s-born women already knew the
OL,16,Fstate pension age was increasing
OL,17,Fthanks to a wide range of public
OL,18,Finformation, including through
OL,19,Fleaflets, education campaigns,
OL,20,Finformation in GP surgeries, on TV,
OL,21,Fradio, cinema and online."
