OL,3,CWaspi campaigners call for a vote in
OL,4,CParliament on compensation
OL,6,FIn 1995, the government announced
OL,7,Fwomen's state pension age would be
OL,8,Fincreased in phases from 2010 over ten
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FAround 3.5 million women were affected
OL,12,Fby the changes.
OL,14,FA Parliamentary and Health Service
OL,15,FOmbudsman report has previously
OL,16,Fsuggested compensation between #1,000
OL,17,Fand nearly #3,000 could be suitable
OL,18,Ffor those affected by how the changes
OL,19,Fwere communicated.
